vote.title: Authorize a budget estimate of the needs and requirements of the Office of the City Auditor for Fiscal Year 2025-2026 in the amount of $3,444,466.00 (subject to vacancy savings of $33,498.00 and final citywide funding adjustments for decisions that will be made on a citywide basis for items such as staff benefits, insurance, Department of Information and Technology Services chargebacks, and other items that may affect all City departmental budgets) - Not to exceed $3,444,466.00 - Financing: General Fund (subject to appropriations)
